1
00:01:31,380 --> 00:01:34,900
=Generation to Generation=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,940
=Episode 10=

3
00:01:42,050 --> 00:01:42,890
Uncle Lei,

4
00:01:43,020 --> 00:01:45,020
you must know about Yin Dai
stealing the credit.

5
00:01:45,620 --> 00:01:46,930
Why did you never tell me?

6
00:01:46,930 --> 00:01:48,096
What good would it have done?

7
00:01:48,850 --> 00:01:50,180
So many people saw it.

8
00:01:50,570 --> 00:01:52,130
Who ever spoke a word of justice?

9
00:01:52,210 --> 00:01:53,660
But with my mother's temperament,

10
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:56,020
how could she endure it?

11
00:01:56,900 --> 00:01:58,490
Your mother was furious at first.

12
00:01:58,980 --> 00:01:59,980
But think about it.

13
00:02:00,290 --> 00:02:01,850
Your aunt was gravely injured

14
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:03,460
and didn't want to be disturbed.

15
00:02:03,850 --> 00:02:04,690
Moreover...

16
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:06,846
My mother had anticipated

17
00:02:06,857 --> 00:02:08,490
that the demonic sect
would seek revenge?

18
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:10,300
Though Nie Hengcheng was killed,

19
00:02:10,980 --> 00:02:13,420
his disciples were vicious and powerful.

20
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:15,980
Yin Dai took the credit,

21
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:18,300
so he naturally had to bear
their retaliation.

22
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:22,100
So,

23
00:02:22,620 --> 00:02:23,460
was Siqi Sect

24
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:25,180
massacred by the demonic sect

25
00:02:25,950 --> 00:02:27,180
because of this?

26
00:02:27,540 --> 00:02:28,380
Yes.

27
00:02:28,860 --> 00:02:30,140
Yang Yi died an untimely death

28
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:31,180
in that massacre.

29
00:02:31,540 --> 00:02:33,300
Only Yang Heying was left.

30
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:35,060
The Yang clan then declined.

31
00:02:36,020 --> 00:02:37,053
All matters in this world

32
00:02:37,100 --> 00:02:38,780
are but reaping what one has sown.

33
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:41,860
Cause and effect cycle endlessly;

34
00:02:41,940 --> 00:02:43,380
retribution never fails.

35
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:44,580
Master.

36
00:02:46,460 --> 00:02:47,300
Zhao.

37
00:02:50,460 --> 00:02:51,300
Xiuming.

38
00:02:54,660 --> 00:02:56,426
The medicine for you
has just been prepared.

39
00:02:56,620 --> 00:02:57,330
Zhao,

40
00:02:57,376 --> 00:02:58,356
take it to your master.

41
00:02:58,460 --> 00:02:59,300
Alright.

42
00:03:01,300 --> 00:03:02,140
Thank you, Xiuming.

43
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:08,060
Master.

44
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:12,660
Yunke,

45
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:14,060
where do you plan

46
00:03:14,220 --> 00:03:15,140
to bury Qiu?

47
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:19,100
After all, we were fellow disciples.

48
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:20,340
I think

49
00:03:20,940 --> 00:03:21,780
we should put him

50
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:23,940
in the ancestral hall of Qingque Sect.

51
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:25,840
The Yin family's ancestral hall?

52
00:03:28,260 --> 00:03:29,100
Master,

53
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:32,460
Uncle Qiu would rather die
than turn back.

54
00:03:32,940 --> 00:03:33,780
Perhaps

55
00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:36,653
he wouldn't wish
to enter the ancestral hall.

56
00:03:38,860 --> 00:03:40,060
Zhao is making a point.

57
00:03:41,060 --> 00:03:41,900
Then I'll find

58
00:03:42,940 --> 00:03:44,060
another place for him.

59
00:03:45,300 --> 00:03:46,140
By the way, Zhao,

60
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:47,860
that day,

61
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:49,340
when you fought that villain,

62
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:50,660
did you see his appearance?

63
00:03:51,980 --> 00:03:52,860
From head to toe,

64
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:54,400
he was tightly covered.

65
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:02,620
But I felt

66
00:04:03,526 --> 00:04:04,752
his bearing was extraordinary.

67
00:04:05,620 --> 00:04:06,940
Extraordinary bearing?

68
00:04:10,620 --> 00:04:13,300
(Chuitian Dock)

69
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:14,140
This saliva

70
00:04:14,260 --> 00:04:15,580
is so miraculous.

71
00:04:16,540 --> 00:04:18,140
I'll go fetch some more for you.

72
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:19,340
No need.

73
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:21,810
Uncle Lei said the saliva
can warm the meridians,

74
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:23,300
but it can only help me recovery

75
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:24,340
to this point.

76
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:27,540
Zhao.

77
00:04:28,460 --> 00:04:29,740
Why did Qian Xueshen

78
00:04:30,380 --> 00:04:32,380
hand over the saliva once you left?

79
00:04:34,700 --> 00:04:35,720
He must be touched

80
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,170
by my sincerity.

81
00:04:38,300 --> 00:04:39,140
And then

82
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:41,580
he died from poison?

83
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:43,210
The demonic sect

84
00:04:43,220 --> 00:04:44,820
had long planted poison in him.

85
00:04:45,180 --> 00:04:46,220
By the time I arrived,

86
00:04:46,231 --> 00:04:47,200
it was already too late.

87
00:04:48,860 --> 00:04:49,700
Alas.

88
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:53,220
Qian Xueshen is gone.

89
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:55,300
Then,

90
00:04:55,420 --> 00:04:56,380
what about Chang?

91
00:04:57,260 --> 00:04:58,380
Did you meet him?

92
00:04:58,620 --> 00:04:59,460
Did he help?

93
00:05:00,660 --> 00:05:01,500
No.

94
00:05:01,580 --> 00:05:02,420
I didn't see him.

95
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:03,940
No one helped me.

96
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:05,260
Who knows where he went?

97
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:08,500
Zhao,

98
00:05:10,180 --> 00:05:11,940
you really didn't go
to the snow mountains?

99
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:13,100
Of course, I didn't.

100
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:16,260
Those snow mountains are far away.

101
00:05:17,140 --> 00:05:19,140
How could I travel back and forth
in half a month?

102
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:24,100
Now that the crisis has passed,

103
00:05:24,340 --> 00:05:26,380
you should rest and recover.

104
00:05:27,300 --> 00:05:28,860
I asked my mother about the treasure

105
00:05:29,279 --> 00:05:30,340
that can cure Nether Aura.

106
00:05:30,620 --> 00:05:31,773
She couldn't remember clearly

107
00:05:31,980 --> 00:05:33,420
and said she needs to look again

108
00:05:33,540 --> 00:05:35,373
through the notes and letters
left by my aunt.

109
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,340
My mother

110
00:05:38,700 --> 00:05:40,540
and my grandfather owe Luoying Valley.

111
00:05:41,060 --> 00:05:42,460
Yet you're still willing to help me.

112
00:05:43,460 --> 00:05:44,620
I'm deeply grateful.

113
00:05:47,380 --> 00:05:49,940
If you truly feel sorry,

114
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:51,260
why not pick

115
00:05:51,660 --> 00:05:53,260
a few treasures from Guangtian Sect

116
00:05:54,860 --> 00:05:56,340
and give them to me?

117
00:05:59,220 --> 00:06:00,980
You can have anything

118
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,580
that Guangtian Sect and I have.

119
00:06:04,220 --> 00:06:05,860
Thank you in advance.

120
00:06:08,260 --> 00:06:09,100
This money

121
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:11,340
is enough for you to open several shops.

122
00:06:14,380 --> 00:06:15,293
Where did it come from?

123
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:17,300
Zhao, you've struck it rich.

124
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,700
Yuzhi's payment to me.

125
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:20,740
The saliva is expensive.

126
00:06:21,246 --> 00:06:22,649
Does that mean Yuzhi's cultivation

127
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:24,660
can recover with the saliva?

128
00:06:25,020 --> 00:06:26,140
He's not fully recovered,

129
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:27,620
but he's been better.

130
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,369
If he wants a complete cure,

131
00:06:29,380 --> 00:06:30,780
he'll still need a healing treasure.

132
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:33,620
Heaven truly envies talent.

133
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:36,340
Uncle said Chang's poison
has also not been fully cured

134
00:06:36,580 --> 00:06:38,130
and still needs an antidote.

135
00:06:42,060 --> 00:06:43,900
Take out the remaining saliva.

136
00:06:44,166 --> 00:06:45,853
- My wounds haven't healed.
- Take it out.

137
00:06:45,866 --> 00:06:47,333
- I can't win.
- Take out the saliva.

138
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:49,300
You soaked in the Wanzai Hot Spring

139
00:06:49,340 --> 00:06:50,180
for quite some time.

140
00:06:50,260 --> 00:06:51,300
Your injuries have healed.

141
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:53,380
Only one of his poisons
remains hard to remove.

142
00:06:53,540 --> 00:06:54,520
So, he still needs rest.

143
00:06:56,020 --> 00:06:56,860
Zhao,

144
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:58,980
that day at the Dusk Palace,

145
00:06:59,060 --> 00:07:01,300
you accused Ning
of being a demonic sect spy.

146
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:02,140
Was that true?

147
00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:03,180
Of course not.

148
00:07:03,620 --> 00:07:04,546
That was just for show.

149
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:06,260
Otherwise, how could we

150
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:07,596
draw them out

151
00:07:07,607 --> 00:07:08,847
and expose the Body Shift plot?

152
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:11,420
That's what I thought.

153
00:07:11,780 --> 00:07:13,420
Chang's acting was so convincing.

154
00:07:14,300 --> 00:07:16,700
That reaction had me thinking
he truly fled in fear of guilt.

155
00:07:17,940 --> 00:07:20,060
Then where is Ning now?

156
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:22,260
Who knows?

157
00:07:22,553 --> 00:07:24,380
Maybe he's hiding somewhere
enjoying himself.

158
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:25,380
Now that he's healed,

159
00:07:26,533 --> 00:07:28,179
he's probably making
a fortune somewhere.

160
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:29,860
Anyway, he never wanted to stay here.

161
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:33,100
Didn't he swear
to avenge his father before?

162
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:34,740
People change.

163
00:07:35,660 --> 00:07:37,860
He might've made another decision.

164
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:50,620
(Li Sect, Youming Path)

165
00:08:15,718 --> 00:08:17,098
(Yu Huiyin, Strategist of Li Sect)

166
00:08:17,109 --> 00:08:17,822
Young...

167
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:19,340
Mu Qingyan,

168
00:08:19,660 --> 00:08:20,740
you're still alive.

169
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:23,540
A mere injury from the Wudu Palm.

170
00:08:24,060 --> 00:08:25,060
What's so hard to cure?

171
00:08:26,740 --> 00:08:28,140
Go back and tell Nie Zhe

172
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:30,240
that the Young Master is back

173
00:08:30,460 --> 00:08:32,060
and will reclaim everything that belongs

174
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:33,180
to the Mu clan.

175
00:08:52,060 --> 00:08:55,620
♪Green robes, oh green robes♪

176
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:58,860
♪Green on the outside, yellow within♪

177
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:02,500
♪The sorrow in my heart♪

178
00:09:02,740 --> 00:09:09,580
♪When will it ever end♪

179
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:40,500
You've always been meticulous

180
00:09:40,540 --> 00:09:41,700
and steady in your actions.

181
00:09:42,660 --> 00:09:45,500
How could this brilliant scheme
to topple Qingque Sect

182
00:09:46,340 --> 00:09:47,660
have failed?

183
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:49,140
Originally,

184
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:51,100
everything was under my control.

185
00:09:51,340 --> 00:09:52,940
However, Cai Pingshu's niece

186
00:09:53,180 --> 00:09:55,220
obtained the antidote to the Body Shift.

187
00:09:55,940 --> 00:09:57,980
Thus, the plan failed.

188
00:09:59,980 --> 00:10:01,540
Cai Pingshu's niece?

189
00:10:02,420 --> 00:10:03,580
How is her martial skill?

190
00:10:03,780 --> 00:10:05,980
She bears much
of Cai Pingshu's former presence.

191
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:09,780
I never expected Cai Pingshu
to leave behind such a remnant

192
00:10:10,180 --> 00:10:12,020
to continue wreaking havoc on our sect.

193
00:10:21,580 --> 00:10:23,100
Chief...

194
00:10:38,660 --> 00:10:41,140
(Sun Ruoshui, Li Sect)

195
00:10:42,820 --> 00:10:43,660
Chief.

196
00:10:43,820 --> 00:10:44,660
Do you know

197
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:46,660
your son has returned?

198
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:49,420
Impossible.

199
00:10:52,620 --> 00:10:53,940
He's back,

200
00:10:54,820 --> 00:10:57,620
unaffected by your poison.

201
00:10:57,780 --> 00:10:58,620
Impossible.

202
00:10:58,700 --> 00:10:59,940
Chief, you must believe me.

203
00:10:59,940 --> 00:11:01,020
This poison has no cure.

204
00:11:01,660 --> 00:11:02,500
Mu...

205
00:11:05,260 --> 00:11:06,100
He is

206
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:07,740
just struggling to live.

207
00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:09,380
He'll die soon.

208
00:11:13,060 --> 00:11:14,460
Of course, I believe you.

209
00:11:15,820 --> 00:11:17,260
But isn't this too coincidental?

210
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:20,180
He appeared

211
00:11:20,780 --> 00:11:22,420
precisely when the strategist

212
00:11:22,620 --> 00:11:23,820
screwed up the plan.

213
00:11:34,380 --> 00:11:36,060
Where did Chang Ning of Chang Fort go?

214
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:38,180
Why is there not the slightest clue

215
00:11:38,307 --> 00:11:39,613
about the item we're looking for?

216
00:11:39,624 --> 00:11:41,220
After Chang Ning went down the mountain,

217
00:11:41,231 --> 00:11:42,333
he vanished without a trace.

218
00:11:42,620 --> 00:11:44,900
I've sent people to search everywhere.

219
00:11:45,100 --> 00:11:46,860
Make sure to find that item.

220
00:11:46,940 --> 00:11:48,060
Understood.

221
00:11:49,220 --> 00:11:51,340
Time to think about how to deal
with Mu Qingyan.

222
00:11:54,780 --> 00:11:55,740
Elder Hufa,

223
00:11:56,300 --> 00:11:57,140
what do you think?

224
00:12:04,940 --> 00:12:07,740
(Hu Fengge, Elder Hufa of Li Sect)

225
00:12:08,340 --> 00:12:09,460
Rest assured, Chief.

226
00:12:10,780 --> 00:12:11,620
Once he comes,

227
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:13,220
he will surely die.

228
00:12:13,860 --> 00:12:15,060
With you and the strategist,

229
00:12:16,020 --> 00:12:17,580
I naturally feel at ease.

230
00:12:36,900 --> 00:12:38,100
Cai Pingshu's niece

231
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:39,740
has such courage.

232
00:12:40,780 --> 00:12:42,140
I was careless and got struck

233
00:12:43,300 --> 00:12:45,060
by Qi Yunke's Huolong Palm.

234
00:12:47,227 --> 00:12:48,427
Had I known this would happen,

235
00:12:49,020 --> 00:12:50,180
I should've gone with you.

236
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:55,420
If you didn't stay in Bliss Palace,

237
00:12:56,540 --> 00:12:57,380
how could I

238
00:12:58,660 --> 00:12:59,980
be at ease outside?

239
00:13:03,660 --> 00:13:05,140
Mu Qingyan has returned

240
00:13:05,820 --> 00:13:07,940
with better martial strength.

241
00:13:09,620 --> 00:13:10,460
Maybe

242
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:12,460
he cultivated some miraculous method.

243
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:14,740
Moreover,

244
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:16,180
Qinong's token has fallen

245
00:13:16,900 --> 00:13:19,220
into Cai Pingshu's niece's hands.

246
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:20,620
I fear

247
00:13:20,940 --> 00:13:22,540
Qinong and Elder Tianji

248
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:25,900
are already dead.

249
00:13:26,860 --> 00:13:28,186
With troubles within and without,

250
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:29,580
in these turbulent times,

251
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:31,460
you and I

252
00:13:33,300 --> 00:13:35,060
must not be careless.

253
00:13:44,466 --> 00:13:46,615
(To Zhao, my daughter)
Yuzhi, my mother has replied.

254
00:13:46,740 --> 00:13:48,820
This treasure is called Jade Sunflower.

255
00:13:48,980 --> 00:13:51,020
It was stolen
from the demonic sect's treasury

256
00:13:51,020 --> 00:13:52,040
by my aunt's close friend.

257
00:13:52,140 --> 00:13:54,300
After curing
the Shi brothers' Nether Aura,

258
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:55,973
its whereabouts became unknown.

259
00:13:56,340 --> 00:13:57,180
So,

260
00:13:58,060 --> 00:13:59,100
there is still no clue.

261
00:13:59,660 --> 00:14:00,500
I suspect

262
00:14:00,859 --> 00:14:02,620
it returned
to the demonic sect's treasury.

263
00:14:02,700 --> 00:14:03,540
How do you know?

264
00:14:04,060 --> 00:14:05,540
My aunt acted with integrity.

265
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:06,553
She wouldn't keep

266
00:14:06,564 --> 00:14:08,020
a demonic sect treasure for herself.

267
00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:10,540
I think after using the Jade Sunflower,

268
00:14:11,100 --> 00:14:12,220
she returned it intact.

269
00:14:12,540 --> 00:14:14,060
Ms. Cai truly was such a person.

270
00:14:17,300 --> 00:14:19,260
Why don't we go steal it

271
00:14:19,460 --> 00:14:21,140
from the demonic sect treasury?

272
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:22,980
The demonic sect is in great turmoil.

273
00:14:23,180 --> 00:14:24,020
It's not that simple.

274
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:25,260
What are you two doing?

275
00:14:28,540 --> 00:14:29,500
What are you two doing?

276
00:14:30,380 --> 00:14:31,980
We're discussing important matters.

277
00:14:32,180 --> 00:14:34,373
What important matter
requires discussing face-to-face?

278
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:35,900
- Lingbo, I...
- Quiet.

279
00:14:35,940 --> 00:14:36,780
I wasn't asking you.

280
00:14:38,660 --> 00:14:39,620
I can't tell you now.

281
00:14:39,700 --> 00:14:40,700
Even to me?

282
00:14:41,460 --> 00:14:42,540
But you can tell her?

283
00:14:43,340 --> 00:14:44,380
Lingbo, actually...

284
00:14:44,380 --> 00:14:45,413
No need to explain to her.

285
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:47,380
Qi Lingbo,

286
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:49,420
have you already forgotten

287
00:14:49,431 --> 00:14:50,660
what you said to me days ago?

288
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:55,700
Yuzhi,

289
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:58,340
do you think I'm too stupid

290
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:00,980
and incompetent to help you?

291
00:15:01,700 --> 00:15:03,460
Is that why you discuss
everything with her?

292
00:15:03,700 --> 00:15:05,020
Or is it you...

293
00:15:05,020 --> 00:15:05,953
You're overthinking it.

294
00:15:06,500 --> 00:15:07,340
I'm not.

295
00:15:08,220 --> 00:15:10,060
I'm the one closest to you.

296
00:15:11,140 --> 00:15:12,500
Yet now, you're not even willing

297
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:14,100
to talk to me.

298
00:15:16,300 --> 00:15:17,140
Well,

299
00:15:18,380 --> 00:15:19,460
sorry to interrupt you two.

300
00:15:20,553 --> 00:15:21,540
I'll take my leave first.

301
00:15:22,700 --> 00:15:24,020
Cai Zhao, stop right there.

302
00:15:24,020 --> 00:15:25,140
Cai Zhao, stop right there!

303
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:27,340
Cai Zhao!

304
00:15:29,980 --> 00:15:30,820
Father.

305
00:15:30,860 --> 00:15:31,700
Uncle.

306
00:15:34,660 --> 00:15:35,500
You're bleeding.

307
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:46,340
Son,

308
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,755
didn't you use to dislike

309
00:15:47,766 --> 00:15:49,500
these gold and silver vulgarities
the most?

310
00:15:49,700 --> 00:15:51,980
Why have people deliver these this time?

311
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:53,460
Zhao likes them.

312
00:15:53,739 --> 00:15:54,820
Compared to refined objects,

313
00:15:55,140 --> 00:15:56,580
she seems to prefer gold and silver.

314
00:15:58,900 --> 00:16:00,500
These are for Zhao?

315
00:16:04,300 --> 00:16:05,420
You like her.

316
00:16:07,500 --> 00:16:08,340
I'm giving her these

317
00:16:08,705 --> 00:16:10,426
to thank her for helping me
find medicine.

318
00:16:11,126 --> 00:16:12,380
I'm still bound by a betrothal.

319
00:16:13,060 --> 00:16:14,233
Father, please don't say that.

320
00:16:14,340 --> 00:16:15,700
Don't harm Zhao's reputation.

321
00:16:16,140 --> 00:16:17,020
Son,

322
00:16:17,060 --> 00:16:17,940
listen to me.

323
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:20,740
A true confidant is hard to find.

324
00:16:21,740 --> 00:16:24,180
Fate is something you must seize.

325
00:16:24,980 --> 00:16:25,820
To be honest,

326
00:16:25,980 --> 00:16:27,300
your betrothal to Lingbo

327
00:16:27,340 --> 00:16:29,980
was decided on a whim
by your mother and Lady Yin.

328
00:16:29,991 --> 00:16:31,545
I've always felt it was inappropriate.

329
00:16:31,660 --> 00:16:32,500
Coincidentally,

330
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:34,660
Lady Yin invited me to discuss matters.

331
00:16:35,180 --> 00:16:36,820
I can just help you annul the betrothal.

332
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:37,940
Father,

333
00:16:38,140 --> 00:16:39,180
a betrothal is serious.

334
00:16:40,260 --> 00:16:42,780
Even if I have no feelings for Lingbo,

335
00:16:42,793 --> 00:16:44,173
I must first report this to Master.

336
00:16:45,020 --> 00:16:45,860
Moreover,

337
00:16:46,086 --> 00:16:47,720
the sect's turmoil
has only just settled,

338
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:49,740
and Senior Qiu just died.

339
00:16:50,486 --> 00:16:51,860
If we break off the betrothal now,

340
00:16:51,940 --> 00:16:53,813
everyone will think Lingbo despises me

341
00:16:53,824 --> 00:16:55,010
for being injured and useless.

342
00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:57,540
How would Lingbo
face herself in the future?

343
00:16:58,900 --> 00:16:59,740
Son,

344
00:16:59,860 --> 00:17:01,940
you always hesitate like this.

345
00:17:02,620 --> 00:17:04,140
What if Zhao leaves you?

346
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:06,460
I still need to cultivate.

347
00:17:07,260 --> 00:17:08,100
Goodbye.

348
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:09,140
You...

349
00:17:18,260 --> 00:17:19,860
Look, the fish have grown quite a bit.

350
00:17:19,980 --> 00:17:20,820
Feed them some more.

351
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:23,340
Look at that one.

352
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:26,980
I heard Yuzhi sent
a lot of valuables to Zhao.

353
00:17:27,100 --> 00:17:28,300
Shijun, do you know about it?

354
00:17:29,500 --> 00:17:31,020
The saliva Zhao sent over

355
00:17:31,020 --> 00:17:32,580
is truly good stuff.

356
00:17:32,660 --> 00:17:33,900
Yuzhi used it in his medicine,

357
00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:35,940
and the cold energy
in his body decreased a lot.

358
00:17:35,980 --> 00:17:36,860
With such great merit,

359
00:17:37,220 --> 00:17:38,700
even sending more treasures

360
00:17:38,820 --> 00:17:39,900
would be only proper.

361
00:17:41,940 --> 00:17:44,300
Zhao did a great service this time.

362
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:47,460
Back then,

363
00:17:47,620 --> 00:17:48,980
Pingshu's grace and bearing

364
00:17:49,100 --> 00:17:50,500
were already breathtaking.

365
00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:53,660
What a surprise that her niece
would be just as outstanding.

366
00:17:54,140 --> 00:17:55,140
So young,

367
00:17:55,293 --> 00:17:56,593
yet calm in the face of trouble,

368
00:17:56,820 --> 00:17:57,700
brave and resourceful,

369
00:17:57,900 --> 00:17:59,166
worthy of great responsibility.

370
00:17:59,380 --> 00:18:02,140
The Cais did a great job in parenting.

371
00:18:03,460 --> 00:18:05,900
Yuzhi also showed
the air of a great general.

372
00:18:06,100 --> 00:18:07,460
If not for his steady response,

373
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:10,020
there might've been complications.

374
00:18:10,460 --> 00:18:11,980
Shijun, have some tea.

375
00:18:16,580 --> 00:18:19,260
Yuzhi naturally carries
my old style and spirit.

376
00:18:24,980 --> 00:18:26,780
I only hate the Nether Aura.

377
00:18:27,540 --> 00:18:28,580
Once I leave,

378
00:18:28,940 --> 00:18:30,380
even if I wear out iron shoes

379
00:18:30,499 --> 00:18:31,533
and spend all my wealth,

380
00:18:31,544 --> 00:18:33,433
I'll try my best to find
more medicine for him.

381
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:34,980
Are you going to leave?

382
00:18:35,700 --> 00:18:36,540
Yes.

383
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:38,420
There are many matters in the sect,

384
00:18:38,580 --> 00:18:40,140
all borne by Xiuzhi alone.

385
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:41,540
I can't set my mind at ease.

386
00:18:42,260 --> 00:18:43,380
Since you're about to leave,

387
00:18:43,380 --> 00:18:44,660
why not take these two days

388
00:18:45,140 --> 00:18:47,900
to set Lingbo and Yuzhi's wedding date?

389
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:50,860
It will also make it easier for Lingbo
to take care of Yuzhi.

390
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:53,340
Well.

391
00:18:54,360 --> 00:18:55,260
There's no rush.

392
00:18:55,300 --> 00:18:56,140
No rush.

393
00:18:57,620 --> 00:18:59,180
Let's wait until Yuzhi recovers.

394
00:18:59,460 --> 00:19:01,180
What if his injury never heals?

395
00:19:03,580 --> 00:19:05,020
Yuzhi is still young.

396
00:19:05,340 --> 00:19:06,300
One year, two years,

397
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:07,700
at most three or five years.

398
00:19:07,700 --> 00:19:08,940
He will recover eventually.

399
00:19:09,460 --> 00:19:10,300
As for the marriage,

400
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:11,780
we can decide later.

401
00:19:45,140 --> 00:19:45,980
Let me see.

402
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:50,620
Milady,

403
00:19:51,020 --> 00:19:52,260
you don't need to do

404
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:54,820
such rough work.

405
00:19:55,380 --> 00:19:57,220
Just have the servants do it.

406
00:19:58,380 --> 00:19:59,460
No.

407
00:19:59,780 --> 00:20:01,620
This is something close to Yuzhi.

408
00:20:02,060 --> 00:20:03,460
How could I let others handle it?

409
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,200
It's getting cold.

410
00:20:05,460 --> 00:20:07,020
I need to finish it quickly for Yuzhi.

411
00:20:07,180 --> 00:20:08,780
No need to care so much about him.

412
00:20:14,220 --> 00:20:15,940
Yuzhi is my fiancé.

413
00:20:16,260 --> 00:20:17,660
If I don't care, who will?

414
00:20:17,860 --> 00:20:19,860
But what if he doesn't have you
in his heart?

415
00:20:22,580 --> 00:20:24,460
Yuzhi and I grew up together.

416
00:20:24,563 --> 00:20:26,032
How could he not have me in his heart?

417
00:20:26,460 --> 00:20:28,060
It's just that he's been injured lately,

418
00:20:28,060 --> 00:20:29,100
and his mood is low.

419
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:31,260
He is a bit more distant than before.

420
00:20:32,260 --> 00:20:33,340
But in the end,

421
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:34,700
we do have a betrothal.

422
00:20:35,060 --> 00:20:36,820
The betrothal was decided by the elders.

423
00:20:36,967 --> 00:20:38,140
It's not impossible to cancel.

424
00:20:39,860 --> 00:20:40,700
Mother,

425
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:45,140
the betrothal was decided
by you and Aunt.

426
00:20:45,506 --> 00:20:47,500
Before Aunt passed away,
she repeatedly instructed

427
00:20:47,540 --> 00:20:48,993
that this betrothal must be honored.

428
00:20:49,100 --> 00:20:50,406
How could we go back on our word?

429
00:20:50,740 --> 00:20:52,300
I made a mistake.

430
00:20:52,740 --> 00:20:54,220
Your aunt passed away so suddenly.

431
00:20:54,300 --> 00:20:55,620
That's why it was decided hastily.

432
00:20:56,260 --> 00:20:58,100
You know Yuzhi better than anyone.

433
00:20:58,300 --> 00:20:59,940
He only loves martial cultivation.

434
00:21:00,046 --> 00:21:01,020
His temperament is cold.

435
00:21:01,380 --> 00:21:02,620
He's not close to you.

436
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:04,460
So,

437
00:21:04,780 --> 00:21:06,326
you told me to restrain my temperament

438
00:21:06,380 --> 00:21:07,740
and get closer to Yuzhi.

439
00:21:08,340 --> 00:21:09,460
After Yuzhi was injured,

440
00:21:09,471 --> 00:21:10,802
I showed care and consideration,

441
00:21:10,813 --> 00:21:11,733
attentive in every way.

442
00:21:12,020 --> 00:21:13,380
I've done all of that.

443
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:15,820
But however you please him,

444
00:21:16,380 --> 00:21:18,180
has he ever been even gentler
toward you?

445
00:21:20,420 --> 00:21:22,460
I can't bear to see you suffer anymore.

446
00:21:22,860 --> 00:21:23,700
From now on,

447
00:21:23,940 --> 00:21:25,140
keep some distance from him.

448
00:21:27,700 --> 00:21:28,540
I'm fine.

449
00:21:29,180 --> 00:21:30,340
I don't think I'm suffering.

450
00:21:31,460 --> 00:21:32,300
Very soon,

451
00:21:32,460 --> 00:21:33,820
Yuzhi's injury will heal,

452
00:21:34,300 --> 00:21:35,980
and everything will get better.

453
00:21:35,980 --> 00:21:37,220
Stop deceiving yourself.

454
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:39,700
The poison he suffered is Nether Aura.

455
00:21:39,980 --> 00:21:41,660
The chance of recovery is slim.

456
00:21:41,980 --> 00:21:43,820
He may never be the Lord.

457
00:21:44,300 --> 00:21:45,740
And you are the Lord's daughter.

458
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:47,820
If your husband
can't love you or protect you,

459
00:21:48,020 --> 00:21:50,260
how will you secure
your position in the sect?

460
00:21:50,860 --> 00:21:51,980
What do you mean?

461
00:21:52,660 --> 00:21:53,700
Do you want me to abandon

462
00:21:53,711 --> 00:21:55,311
my fiancé because of his incompetence

463
00:21:55,322 --> 00:21:56,740
and marry another man just like you?

464
00:21:56,740 --> 00:21:57,580
Nonsense.

465
00:21:57,740 --> 00:21:59,700
Everything I do is for your own good.

466
00:21:59,966 --> 00:22:02,180
The Yins have operated
within the sect for generations.

467
00:22:02,180 --> 00:22:03,880
Are we to watch helplessly
as someone else

468
00:22:03,900 --> 00:22:05,260
takes charge of the sect?

469
00:22:05,260 --> 00:22:06,140
So what?

470
00:22:06,540 --> 00:22:07,660
What do you take me for?

471
00:22:08,140 --> 00:22:09,700
A puppet to maintain the Yins' power?

472
00:22:09,700 --> 00:22:11,980
Enough. How dare you accuse me?

473
00:22:19,740 --> 00:22:21,260
When I was lazy in cultivation before,

474
00:22:22,340 --> 00:22:24,340
you failed to urge me to improve

475
00:22:24,860 --> 00:22:27,020
and even told me stories
of powerful women

476
00:22:27,300 --> 00:22:28,700
meeting tragic ends.

477
00:22:29,700 --> 00:22:30,660
But now,

478
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:32,780
I truly envy Cai Zhao.

479
00:22:33,660 --> 00:22:35,060
When the sect faced a crisis,

480
00:22:35,140 --> 00:22:36,220
she was brave and fearless,

481
00:22:36,540 --> 00:22:37,860
able to turn the tide.

482
00:22:38,140 --> 00:22:40,420
She can do what she wants to do.

483
00:22:40,513 --> 00:22:42,569
She doesn't need others
to love her or protect her.

484
00:22:42,580 --> 00:22:44,220
She can protect herself.

485
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:46,740
Milady,

486
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:49,180
Lady Yin is only worried about you.

487
00:22:49,660 --> 00:22:51,060
Is she worried about me,

488
00:22:51,140 --> 00:22:53,020
or does she look down on me?

489
00:22:53,740 --> 00:22:55,460
You were just like Grandfather,

490
00:22:55,460 --> 00:22:58,020
believing women cannot be lords,

491
00:22:58,460 --> 00:23:00,180
insisting on finding
a powerful husband,

492
00:23:00,540 --> 00:23:02,420
until you met Cai Pingshu.

493
00:23:02,620 --> 00:23:03,653
Then you finally realized

494
00:23:03,860 --> 00:23:05,740
that women too can be powerful,

495
00:23:06,180 --> 00:23:08,060
brave, and unstoppable.

496
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:12,900
So, you and Aunt harbored resentment,

497
00:23:13,420 --> 00:23:15,020
targeting the Cais at every turn,

498
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:17,540
even using Cai Pingshu's tragic death
to warn me,

499
00:23:17,780 --> 00:23:19,189
wanting me to walk the same path

500
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:20,740
of attaching myself to others as you.

501
00:23:20,740 --> 00:23:22,082
What's so great about Cai Pingshu?

502
00:23:22,093 --> 00:23:23,426
She died young.

503
00:23:23,580 --> 00:23:26,100
If I could die as spectacularly
as Cai Pingshu,

504
00:23:26,100 --> 00:23:27,420
an early death would be worth it.

505
00:23:32,180 --> 00:23:33,020
Lingbo.

506
00:23:34,020 --> 00:23:35,620
What did I say wrong?

507
00:23:36,340 --> 00:23:38,460
It was all Grandfather's selfishness

508
00:23:38,780 --> 00:23:40,900
that caused so many tragedies
and disasters.

509
00:23:41,180 --> 00:23:42,580
For the Yin's power,

510
00:23:42,660 --> 00:23:44,100
for the position of the Lord's wife,

511
00:23:44,220 --> 00:23:46,140
how many more people must you sacrifice?

512
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:49,140
Lingbo...

513
00:23:51,260 --> 00:23:52,100
Milady.

514
00:23:52,980 --> 00:23:53,820
Lingbo?

515
00:23:54,460 --> 00:23:55,300
Milady.

516
00:23:57,260 --> 00:23:58,100
Lady Yin.

517
00:24:02,100 --> 00:24:03,420
Dalou, why are you here?

518
00:24:04,460 --> 00:24:07,140
I heard you were struck
by the Chaos Needle.

519
00:24:07,460 --> 00:24:09,940
Why aren't you resting?

520
00:24:10,420 --> 00:24:11,540
Thank you for your concern.

521
00:24:12,260 --> 00:24:13,460
I'm already much better.

522
00:24:14,500 --> 00:24:15,580
Master ordered me to come

523
00:24:16,300 --> 00:24:18,460
and return this to you.

524
00:24:31,420 --> 00:24:32,860
The Clearing Pill.-

525
00:25:26,460 --> 00:25:30,620
(Grave of Qiu Renjie)

526
00:25:47,060 --> 00:25:48,140
Since you're here,

527
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:50,260
come pay your respects.

528
00:25:54,540 --> 00:25:56,820
Why did you have Dalou return the pill,

529
00:25:56,966 --> 00:25:58,106
yet you didn't come yourself?

530
00:26:00,220 --> 00:26:01,140
Since that day,

531
00:26:01,300 --> 00:26:03,180
you've been avoiding me.

532
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:06,180
Are you bothered by my past with Qiu?

533
00:26:07,386 --> 00:26:09,100
When he pretended to be you,
we did not...

534
00:26:09,100 --> 00:26:10,980
I know you did not cross any boundaries.

535
00:26:11,340 --> 00:26:12,780
Then why is it?

536
00:26:13,300 --> 00:26:15,220
Qiu held deep resentment
toward my father.

537
00:26:15,540 --> 00:26:16,820
He left the sect long ago.

538
00:26:16,859 --> 00:26:18,180
One-sided words cannot be trusted.

539
00:26:18,180 --> 00:26:19,020
Dear,

540
00:26:19,780 --> 00:26:21,260
even if Qiu Renjie wronged everyone,

541
00:26:21,260 --> 00:26:22,740
he'd never wrong you.

542
00:26:23,900 --> 00:26:25,660
If he truly intended to humiliate you,

543
00:26:25,660 --> 00:26:26,900
he would not have repeatedly

544
00:26:26,900 --> 00:26:28,340
kept you outside his door.

545
00:26:29,740 --> 00:26:31,060
If he truly were a spy,

546
00:26:31,420 --> 00:26:32,260
even for appearances,

547
00:26:32,380 --> 00:26:34,100
he would've pretended
to be close to you.

548
00:26:35,060 --> 00:26:36,620
But he refused to approach you at all,

549
00:26:37,700 --> 00:26:39,060
just to protect your reputation.

550
00:26:39,060 --> 00:26:40,820
That was what let Yuzhi see the flaw.

551
00:26:42,740 --> 00:26:43,580
Not to mention

552
00:26:44,260 --> 00:26:45,420
that Clearing Pill.

553
00:26:47,220 --> 00:26:48,380
Are you blaming me

554
00:26:48,540 --> 00:26:50,180
for keeping the pill all these years?

555
00:26:50,900 --> 00:26:52,700
Then what about you,

556
00:26:52,700 --> 00:26:54,180
going to Luoying Valley every year,

557
00:26:54,180 --> 00:26:55,380
thinking of a bedridden woman?

558
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:13,300
Forget it.

559
00:27:31,660 --> 00:27:36,180
(Grave of Qiu Renjie)

560
00:27:40,940 --> 00:27:46,420
(Qinglong Altar)

561
00:27:54,500 --> 00:27:57,340
(Lian Shisan, Li Sect)

562
00:28:10,420 --> 00:28:14,620
(You Guanyue, Master of Qinglong Altar)

563
00:28:16,460 --> 00:28:17,700
Today is Master You's birthday.

564
00:28:18,140 --> 00:28:19,740
There should surely be many guests,

565
00:28:20,020 --> 00:28:21,220
lively and bustling.

566
00:28:24,260 --> 00:28:26,380
Thank you all for coming...

567
00:28:27,980 --> 00:28:28,820
Where is everyone?

568
00:28:30,213 --> 00:28:31,500
Why isn't there a single person?

569
00:28:33,140 --> 00:28:34,133
This is bad, Master You.

570
00:28:34,813 --> 00:28:36,860
There are rumors
that you colluded with Mu Qingyan,

571
00:28:36,871 --> 00:28:38,542
just like your adoptive father,
Elder Qiu,

572
00:28:38,553 --> 00:28:39,329
intending to rebel.

573
00:28:39,340 --> 00:28:40,420
To avoid suspicion,

574
00:28:40,700 --> 00:28:41,740
no one dares to come.

575
00:28:41,860 --> 00:28:42,700
What?

576
00:28:44,060 --> 00:28:44,900
Me?

577
00:28:46,020 --> 00:28:47,140
Rebel?

578
00:28:47,980 --> 00:28:49,300
Isn't this slandering me?

579
00:28:49,300 --> 00:28:51,740
This is more unjust
than snow falling in midsummer.

580
00:28:55,980 --> 00:28:56,820
Shisan,

581
00:28:58,300 --> 00:28:59,180
bring paper and ink.

582
00:28:59,820 --> 00:29:00,660
Yes.

583
00:29:14,180 --> 00:29:16,620
This petition of grievance to the Chief

584
00:29:17,580 --> 00:29:18,780
must show some sincerity.

585
00:29:27,260 --> 00:29:28,100
Shisan,

586
00:29:28,853 --> 00:29:30,260
let me see your long, slender hand.

587
00:29:35,140 --> 00:29:35,980
What are you doing?

588
00:29:42,140 --> 00:29:43,460
Dear Chief,

589
00:29:43,780 --> 00:29:45,820
since joining the Li Sect,

590
00:29:46,100 --> 00:29:49,500
I've only known the Nie clan,
never the Mu clan.

591
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:54,260
My loyalty to you

592
00:29:55,220 --> 00:29:58,380
is wholehearted and true.

593
00:30:03,180 --> 00:30:04,420
It's Master You's birthday.

594
00:30:04,860 --> 00:30:06,700
Why is it so desolate?

595
00:30:12,860 --> 00:30:14,340
Mr. Yu, you're here.

596
00:30:14,860 --> 00:30:16,780
My Qinglong Altar is truly honored.

597
00:30:17,100 --> 00:30:18,100
I heard that you stirred

598
00:30:18,100 --> 00:30:19,620
the Six Sects into discord

599
00:30:20,060 --> 00:30:22,420
and left them with a mess with ghostly

600
00:30:22,420 --> 00:30:23,460
and unfathomable methods.

601
00:30:23,780 --> 00:30:26,300
What a remarkable deed.

602
00:30:26,580 --> 00:30:28,100
What have I done to deserve

603
00:30:28,980 --> 00:30:31,260
your personal congratulations?

604
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:34,420
I...

605
00:30:34,540 --> 00:30:36,060
I'm so moved that I could cry.

606
00:30:37,140 --> 00:30:37,980
Li Yi.

607
00:30:39,540 --> 00:30:41,380
The Chief heard it's your birthday

608
00:30:41,620 --> 00:30:43,300
and had someone find

609
00:30:43,620 --> 00:30:45,940
Elder Qiu's spear from the treasury

610
00:30:46,180 --> 00:30:47,460
as a gift.

611
00:30:51,260 --> 00:30:53,020
Master You, do not overthink it.

612
00:30:53,860 --> 00:30:55,180
The Chief means

613
00:30:55,740 --> 00:30:57,460
that Elder Qiu's position

614
00:30:57,780 --> 00:31:00,180
will sooner or later be yours.

615
00:31:00,180 --> 00:31:01,740
The Qinglong Altar guards the first line

616
00:31:01,740 --> 00:31:02,980
of our Li Sect.

617
00:31:03,260 --> 00:31:05,860
We will rely on you even more.

618
00:31:06,980 --> 00:31:08,980
Thanks to the Chief.

619
00:31:09,660 --> 00:31:10,580
Thanks, Mr. Yu.

620
00:31:10,980 --> 00:31:12,340
My subordinate, Li Yi,

621
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:15,020
has long admired your talent.

622
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:17,340
Today, I'll do a small favor

623
00:31:17,340 --> 00:31:18,780
and let him stay here

624
00:31:18,900 --> 00:31:21,100
to seek guidance from you.

625
00:31:21,540 --> 00:31:23,260
(Li Yi, Li Sect)
I long for your advice.

626
00:31:28,420 --> 00:31:29,660
Master You is unwilling.

627
00:31:29,980 --> 00:31:30,820
Then, let's go.

628
00:31:30,860 --> 00:31:31,980
With Li's help,

629
00:31:32,260 --> 00:31:34,260
we'll surely be like a tiger with wings.

630
00:31:34,580 --> 00:31:37,740
I won't fail the trust
of Mr. Yu and the Chief.

631
00:31:44,500 --> 00:31:45,420
Nonsense.

632
00:31:45,660 --> 00:31:46,540
Guidance?

633
00:31:46,980 --> 00:31:48,380
He's clearly here to spy on me.

634
00:31:50,060 --> 00:31:51,660
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang)

635
00:31:53,100 --> 00:31:53,940
Father.

636
00:31:55,140 --> 00:31:56,100
Why are you here?

637
00:32:00,460 --> 00:32:01,380
Darn it.

638
00:32:02,660 --> 00:32:04,100
Who wants to harm me?

639
00:32:11,740 --> 00:32:15,700
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang,
Elder Tianquan)

640
00:32:19,700 --> 00:32:20,540
Father,

641
00:32:21,340 --> 00:32:22,420
you're magnanimous.

642
00:32:23,580 --> 00:32:24,620
Don't blame me.

643
00:32:30,520 --> 00:32:31,410
Who?

644
00:32:31,420 --> 00:32:32,260
Who dares to hit me?

645
00:32:34,980 --> 00:32:36,380
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang)

646
00:32:43,980 --> 00:32:44,820
Father,

647
00:32:45,820 --> 00:32:46,820
don't harm me.

648
00:32:47,820 --> 00:32:48,700
You're magnanimous.

649
00:32:59,020 --> 00:32:59,900
(Spirit Tablet)

650
00:33:01,940 --> 00:33:02,820
Father,

651
00:33:03,580 --> 00:33:05,060
I know you died unjustly.

652
00:33:05,500 --> 00:33:07,300
But my life in the sect
isn't easy either.

653
00:33:07,500 --> 00:33:08,340
Every day,

654
00:33:08,900 --> 00:33:10,220
danger lurks everywhere.

655
00:33:10,333 --> 00:33:11,486
I'm like walking on thin ice.

656
00:33:11,660 --> 00:33:14,580
I'm already 31 this year,

657
00:33:15,380 --> 00:33:16,700
yet I still haven't married Xing.

658
00:33:16,780 --> 00:33:18,380
You don't even have a grandson.

659
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:20,380
If you kill me,

660
00:33:20,980 --> 00:33:21,820
there will be no one

661
00:33:23,380 --> 00:33:24,780
left to worship you.

662
00:33:25,260 --> 00:33:26,940
Father, you're magnanimous.

663
00:33:26,980 --> 00:33:27,820
I'll kowtow to you.

664
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:39,453
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang)
Rebel!

665
00:33:39,540 --> 00:33:40,380
I...

666
00:33:42,580 --> 00:33:43,420
Get lost!

667
00:33:44,540 --> 00:33:45,740
What a jerk!

668
00:33:46,220 --> 00:33:47,060
Go die!

669
00:33:48,580 --> 00:33:51,620
(Qinglong Altar)

670
00:34:37,241 --> 00:34:47,901
=Generation to Generation=

671
00:35:06,661 --> 00:35:11,071
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

672
00:35:11,636 --> 00:35:16,251
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

673
00:35:16,591 --> 00:35:21,156
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

674
00:35:21,681 --> 00:35:25,981
♪Free to wander in the world♪

675
00:35:28,926 --> 00:35:33,626
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

676
00:35:34,151 --> 00:35:38,441
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

677
00:35:39,101 --> 00:35:43,131
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

678
00:35:43,446 --> 00:35:48,571
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

679
00:35:49,146 --> 00:35:53,956
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

680
00:35:54,171 --> 00:35:58,341
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

681
00:35:59,066 --> 00:36:03,001
♪I freely roam in the world♪

682
00:36:03,501 --> 00:36:08,776
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

683
00:36:31,506 --> 00:36:36,636
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

684
00:36:37,001 --> 00:36:41,371
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

685
00:36:41,636 --> 00:36:45,766
♪I freely roam in the world♪

686
00:36:45,951 --> 00:36:51,526
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
